irus fuels anti-Chinese discrimination in Africa |url=https://www.dw.com/en/coronavirus-fuels-anti-chinese-discrimination-in-africa/av-52428454 |publisher=[[Deutsche Welle]] |date=19 February 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"ttiz2\">{{cite news |title=Chinese industrial workers subject to mandatory coronavirus isolation in Ethiopia |url=https://www.panapress.com/Chinese-industrial-workers-subje-a_630630164-lang2.html |work=Panapress.com |date=28 February 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"iOyUQ\">{{cite news |title=Italy Shows Just How Crazy Coronavirus Panic Can Get |url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/italy-shows-just-how-crazy-coronavirus-panic-can-get |work=[[The Daily Beast]] |date=29 February 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"FFsxo\">{{cite news |title=Italians Are Being Treated as a Risk Abroad Over Coronavirus |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/italians-are-being-treated-as-a-risk-abroad-over-coronavirus-11582913454 |work=[[The Wall Street Journal]] |date=28 February 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"HWwxd\">{{cite web |url=https://thethaiger.com/coronavirus/thailand-increasingly-blaming-caucasians-for-coronavirus-crisis |title=Thailand increasingly blaming caucasians for coronavirus crisis |first=Greeley |last=Pulitzer |date=23 March 2020 |website=The Thaiger}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"D70pk\">{{cite web |url=https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/01/559942/some-malaysians-calling-ban-chinese-tourists |title=Some Malaysians calling for ban on Chinese tourists |last=Solhi |first=Farah |date=26 January 2020 |work=[[New Straits Times]] |access-date=12 February 2020 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200127152306/https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2020/01/559942/some-malaysians-calling-ban-chinese-tourists |archive-date=27 January 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"7hjPP\">{{cite news |title=Calm urged as anti-Chinese sentiment felt in New Zealand |url=https://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=12304816 |access-date=6 February 2020 |work=[[The New Zealand Herald]]