ex.html COVID-19] ([https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/about/index.html Q&A]) by the [[Centers for Disease Control and Prevention|U.S. Centers for Disease Control]]\n* [https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/emres/2019_ncov.html Coronavirus Disease 2019] ([https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/docs/2018-130/pdfs/2018-130.pdf?id=10.26616/NIOSHPUB2018130 Q&A]) by the [[National Institute for Occupational Safety and Health]]\n\n===Directories===\n\n* [https://curlie.org/Health/Conditions_and_Diseases/Respiratory_Disorders/COVID-19/ COVID-19 Directory on Curlie]\n* [https://openmd.com/directory/covid-19 COVID-19 Resource Directory on OpenMD]\n\n===Data and graphs===\n\n* [https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019/situation-reports/ Coronavirus disease (COVID-2019) situation reports] and [https://who.sprinklr.com/ map] by the World Health Organization\n* [https://www.arcgis.com/apps/opsdashboard/index.html#/bda7594740fd40299423467b48e9ecf6 Coronavirus COVID-19 Global Cases] and [https://github.com/CSSEGISandData/COVID-19 historical data] created by [[Lauren Gardner (scientist)|Lauren Gardner]] at [[Johns Hopkins University]]\n* [https://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/publications-data/download-todays-data-geographic-distribution-covid-19-cases-worldwide Historical data about COVID-19 cases] published by the [[European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control|European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control (ECDC)]]\n* [http://unwfp.maps.arcgis.com/apps/opsdashboard/index.html#/42b8837bb25049b9b1f69a9555d55808 World Travel Restrictions] based on [[World Food Programme|WFP]] data\n* [https://covid.observer Coronavirus Observer] based on [[Johns Hopkins University]] data\n* [https://www.worldometers.info/coronavirus/ Covid-19 coronavirus pandemic] published by the [[worldometers.info|Worldometer]] website\n* [https://ourworldindata.org/coronavirus Coronavirus Disease (COVID-19) Statistics and Research] published by the [[Our World in Data]] website\n* [https://covid19.healthdata.org/united-states-of-america COVID-19 Projections] for many different countries published by [[Institute for Health Metrics and Evaluation]]\n* [https://sites.google.com/site/pandemicdata/ Historical data with additional computations and graphs in user-friendly spreadsheet format] created by [https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Dianelos Dianelos Georgoudis]\n\n===Medical journals===\n\n* [https://jamanetwork.com/journals/jama/pages/coronavirus-alert Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19)] by [[JAMA (journal)|JAMA]]\n* [https://www.bmj.com/coronavirus Coronavirus: News and Resources] by [[BMJ (company)|BMJ Publishing Group]]\n* [https://www.elsevier.com/connect/coronavirus-information-center Novel Coronavirus Information Center] by [[Elsevier]]\n* [https://www.thelancet.com/coronavirus COVID-19 Resource Centre] by [[The Lancet]]\n* [https://www.springernature.com/gp/researchers/campaigns/coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 and COVID-19] by [[Nature (journal)|Nature]]\n* [https://www.nejm.org/coronavirus Coronavirus (Covid-19)] by [[New England Journal of Medicine]]\n* [https://novel-coronavirus.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/ Covid-19: Novel Coronavirus] by [[Wiley (publisher)|Wiley Publishing]]\n\n{{2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic|short=true}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2019-20 coronavirus pandemic}}\n[[Category:2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic| ]]\n[[Category:2010s disease outbreaks]]\n[[Category:2019 disasters in Asia]]\n[[Category:2019 disasters in China]]\n[[Category:2019 health disasters]]\n[[Category:2019 in international relations]]\n[[Category:2020 disasters in Asia]]\n[[Category:2020 health disasters]]\n[[Category:2020 in international relations]]\n[[Category:2020s disease outbreaks]]\n[[Category:21st-century epidemics]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:Atypical pneumonias]]\n[[Category:Current events]]\n[[Category:December 2019 events in China]]\n[[Category:February 2020 events in China]]\n[[Category:Health disasters in China]]\n[